rdprrap-installer plan
======================

Install directory
  %ProgramFiles%\RDP Wrapper\

Wrapper DLLs (built_name -> installed_name)
  termwrap_dll.dll -> termwrap.dll
  umwrap_dll.dll -> umwrap.dll
  endpwrap_dll.dll -> endpwrap.dll

ServiceDll registration
  HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\TermService\Parameters\ServiceDll = %ProgramFiles%\RDP Wrapper\termwrap.dll (REG_EXPAND_SZ)

Registry keys touched (all under HKLM)
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\TermService\Parameters
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\Licensing Core
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\AddIns
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\AddIns\Clip Redirector
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\AddIns\DND Redirector
  SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\AddIns\Dynamic VC
  SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon
  SOFTWARE\rdprrap\Installer

Firewall rules (inbound, profile=any)
  rdprrap-RDP-TCP tcp/3389
  rdprrap-RDP-UDP udp/3389

Uninstall behavior
  Restore original ServiceDll from installer-state key
  Remove wrapper DLLs + install directory
  Remove firewall rules
  Restart TermService
